== Configuration ==

=== Services ===

==== OpenRC ====

To immediately start the logmein-hamachi service:

{{RootCmd|rc-service logmein-hamachi start}}

To have the service start during the default runlevel (system boot), enter:

{{RootCmd|rc-update add logmein-hamachi default}}

=== Server ===

{{RootCmd|hamachi login}}

{{RootCmd|hamachi set-nick gentoo}}

{{RootCmd|hamachi create 12345678}}

Set a strong password

{{RootCmd|hamachi set-ip-mode ipv4}}

To show the PID, IP, status, client, ID, and nickname:

{{RootCmd|hamachi}}

=== Client ===

{{RootCmd|hamachi login}}

{{RootCmd|hamachi set-nick alsogentoo}}

{{RootCmd|hamachi do-join 12345678}}

Enter the server's strong password.

